<paragraph blockId="20.[177,1086,297,588]" pageId="20" pageNumber="787">D i a g n o s i s.Alarge specieswith pronotum setose on disc, rusty brown with margins lighter brown, elytra setose, elytral puncturation completely confused, interstices smooth, setose, lateral two furrows on elytra hardly perceptible, rest of elytra even, apex of male clypeus extended, narrow with acute tip.</paragraph>
